centralka_fall_down_2024

Can't parkour?

Are you constantly falling?

This is a map especially for you! Here you need to go down to the bottom. Each button gives a different amount of hp.

White - 1000 hp

Green - 300 hp

Yellow - 200 hp

Red - 100 hp

Black - 1 hp

Counter-terrorists have immortality.
At the very bottom there is a button that turns off the music and turns on the background sound.

Also, each of these levels has its own fun music, enjoy the map!
